name: Penalty for signing false document
text:
[§414-20]  Penalty for signing false document.  (a)  A person commits an offense if the person signs a document the person knows is false in any material respect with intent that the document be delivered to the department director for filing.
     (b)  An offense under this section is a class C felony. [L 2000, c 244, pt of §1]
